{"arkId":"cl010113073","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010113073","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Montre ovale","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Montre ovale"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Henri IV (1589-1610) (Occident-\u003ERenaissance-\u003Edynastie des Bourbons)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1600 - 1615","currentLocation":"Richelieu, [OArt] Salle 531 - Paul Garnier, Vitrine 2","room":"Salle 531, Aile Aile Richelieu, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1600,"endYear":1615,"imprecision":"","text":"D\u00e9but du XVIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Chesnon, Salomon","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","dates":[{"date":"1572","place":"Blois","type":"date de naissance"},{"date":"1639","place":"Blois","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"Horloger","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 7025","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"horlogerie ; montre","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Montre ovale ; bo\u00eetier compos\u00e9 de deux couvercles \u00e0 charni\u00e8re, d\u0027une carrure grav\u00e9e et d\u0027armatures en laiton. Couvercle du cadran repr\u00e9sentant Diane et ses chiens, tenant une fl\u00e8che et portant un carquois ; celui du mouvement figure Junon en compagnie de son paon, tenant un b\u00e2ton autour duquel s\u0027enroule un serpent ; les d\u00e9esses apparaissent sur un fond de rinceaux \u00e0 fleurs de fraisier, peupl\u00e9s d\u0027oiseaux, d\u0027\u00e9cureuils et de papillons. Les deux repr\u00e9sentations sont d\u0027apr\u00e8s des estampes d\u0027Etienne Delaune. L\u0027int\u00e9rieur des couvercles grav\u00e9 de guirlandes de feuillages ; frise de la carrure pr\u00e9sentant deux chiens courant, l\u0027un apr\u00e8s un li\u00e8vre, l\u0027autre derri\u00e8re un sanglier. Pendant en forme de chapiteau. Cadran grav\u00e9 de rinceaux fleuris parmi lesquels Junon est allong\u00e9e pr\u00e8s de son paon. A l\u0027int\u00e9rieur de l\u0027anneau r\u00e9serv\u00e9 est grav\u00e9e la Mort de Pyrame et Thisb\u00e9 d\u0027apr\u00e8s E. Delaune. Mouvement ajust\u00e9 dans la bo\u00eete, muni d\u0027un \u00e9chappement \u00e0 verge, d\u0027une fus\u00e9e avec corde \u00e0 boyau. Coq et cliquet reperc\u00e9s et grav\u00e9s de rinceaux fleuris.","inscriptions":"Signature : \r ; mouvement sign\u00e9 : Salomon Chesnon\/A Blois","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"6,4","displayDimension":"6,4 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"3,2","displayDimension":"3,2 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Epaisseur","value":"2,3","displayDimension":"2,3 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : argent\r\nMat\u00e9riau : laiton","placeOfCreation":"Blois (Centre-\u003ELoir-et-Cher = Loir et Cher)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Collection Gavet ; collection Paul Garnier (1834-1916), \u00e0 Paris. Don Paul Garnier, en 1916.","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"M. Garnier, Paul ","note":"","role":", Donateur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"don","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date du d\u00e9cret","value":"19\/06\/1916","startYear":1916,"endYear":1916}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","longTermLoanTo":"","index":{"Mode d\u0027acquisition":[{"value":"don"}],"period":[{"value":"Henri IV (1589-1610)"}],"place":[{"value":"Blois"}],"objectType":[{"value":"horlogerie"},{"value":"montre"}]},"bibliography":[{"bibliographyRef":"Rohou, Julie (dir.), Graver la Renaissance : Etienne Delaune et les arts d\u00e9coratifs, cat. exp. (Ecouen (Externe, France), Mus\u00e9e de la Renaissance - ch\u00e2teau d\u0027Ecouen, 16 octobre 2019 - 3 f\u00e9vrier 2020), Paris, R\u00e9union des mus\u00e9es nationaux-Grand Palais, 2019","bibliographyDate":"2019","bibliographyDetail":"p. 165-167, n\u00b0 74","comparison":false},{"bibliographyRef":"RMN, Mus\u00e9e du Louvre (dir.), Un temps d\u0027exub\u00e9rance. Les arts d\u00e9coratifs sous Louis XIII et Anne d\u0027Autriche, cat. exp. (Paris, Galeries nationales du Grand Palais, 11 Avril 2002 - 08 Juillet 2002), Paris, RMN, 2002","bibliographyDate":"2002","bibliographyDetail":"p. 294","comparison":false},{"bibliographyRef":"Cardinal, Catherine, Les montres et horloges de table du mus\u00e9e du Louvre, Tome 2, Paris, RMN, 2000","bibliographyDate":"2000","bibliographyDetail":"n\u00b0 84","comparison":false}],"exhibition":[{"value":"La fabrique des mod\u00e8les : Etienne Delaune et les arts d\u00e9coratifs de la Renaissance, Ecouen (Externe, France), Mus\u00e9e de la Renaissance - ch\u00e2teau d\u0027Ecouen, 16\/10\/2019 - 03\/02\/2020 "},{"value":"Marie de M\u00e9dicis, un gouvernement par les arts, Blois (France), Ch\u00e2teau et Mus\u00e9es de Blois, 29\/11\/2003 - 28\/03\/2004 "}],"relatedWork":[],"image":[{"urlImage":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/large\/0000000021\/0000113073\/0001050106_OG.JPG","urlThumbnail":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/small\/0000000021\/0000113073\/0001050106_OG.JPG","copyright":"\u00a9 2019 GrandPalaisRmn (mus\u00e9e du Louvre) \/ St\u00e9phane Mar\u00e9challe","type":"","position":0},{"urlImage":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/media\/cache\/large\/0000000021\/0000113073\/000105010